---
title: Golden Coconut Pork & Veggie Udon Noodles  with Crushed Peanuts & Coriander
description:  Everything is glittering and golden tonight, with ropes of pork udon noodles coiled in a coconutty broth. It’s brimming withdelicious pops of veggies like baby broccoli and carrot. All you need is a sprinkle of peanuts to make this dish shine!

*We’ve replaced the green beans in this recipe with asparagus due to local ingredient availability. It’ll be just as delicious, just follow your recipe card!*
